		<title>Why Doesn&#8217;t My Story Read Like a Published Novel&#8211;A Reader&#8217;s Question</title>
		<link>http://theeditorsblog.net/2015/01/11/why-doesnt-my-story-read-like-a-published-novel-a-readers-question/</link>
		<comments>http://theeditorsblog.net/2015/01/11/why-doesnt-my-story-read-like-a-published-novel-a-readers-question/#comments</comments>
