		<link>http://theeditorsblog.net/2014/10/12/push-yourself-to-new-heights-or-explore-the-depths/</link>
		<comments>http://theeditorsblog.net/2014/10/12/push-yourself-to-new-heights-or-explore-the-depths/#comments</comments>
